# Summary
Amplitude Activation's Meta Pixel streaming integration enables forwarding Amplitude events to Meta Pixel, requiring Meta Pixel ID and Conversions API Access Token for setup, with support for mapping user properties to Meta Pixel Customer Information Parameters and sending additional properties as Custom Data Parameters.

